---
title: Autumn Chicken Dinner with Roasted Apples and Brussels
description: We've spruced up the everyday sheet pan dinner with crisp apples and Brussel sprouts. Savoury cranberry chutney is the perfect pairing for tonight's fall-inspired dinner!
